videos.description: Eric Bledsoe drives the lane and tosses up a lob to Steven Adams who goes up and stuffs down a dunk with one hand for the Pelicans.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bledsoe lobs to Adams for a dunk in the lane) 2021/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bledsoe lobs to Adams for a dunk in the lane

videos.description: Kyle Lowry gets knocked down and is called for a Flagrant 1 foul as he reaches across the legs of Eric Bledsoe and trips him in an attempt to tip the ball away.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lowry called for Flagrant 1 after tripping Bledsoe) 2021/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lowry called for Flagrant 1 after tripping Bledsoe

videos.description: Lonzo Ball throws up a lob to Zion Williamson from the 3-point line for a two-handed dunk for the Pelicans.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lonzo lobs to Zion for a Pelicans slam) 2021/01/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lonzo lobs to Zion for a Pelicans slam

videos.description: Fred VanVleet misses a 3-pointer, but gets a second chance at it from the top of the key and drains it.
